        <item>
          <title>Netflix Suffers Big Data Breach: Stranger Things Season 5 Spoilers Leaked Online</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Netflix has suffered another big data breach, with spoilers for Stranger Things season 5 leaking online. The leak comes six months after a similar incident, and the streaming giant is taking aggressive action to take down social media posts and YouTube videos related to the leak.]]></description>
